    "<p>Editor of the <em>Art News</em> during the critical years of Abstract Expressionism.": [],
    "Frankfurter was the son of Moritz Frankfurter and Freda Heyman (Frankfurter) of Chicago.": [],
    "He attended the Boy's Latin School in Chicago followed by one year at Princeton University.": [],
    "He transferred to Humboldt University, Berlin, where he was awarded an undergraduate degree and graduate degree from the Institut f\u00fcr Kunstgeschichte (Institute for Art History).": [
